umbnail":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-256eced1603068ccd0bdb0801e9386ed_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545965331,"updated_time":1545965405,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":25,"content":"\u003cp\u003e如果题主真能证明得出，我就在本回答的评论中随机抽中一位关注我的知友，赠送Feather AS D2 不锈钢手动剃须刀一把，绝不食言。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f44aef4223773b8e1d742eb31c19607b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f44aef4223773b8e1d742eb31c19607b_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-3aeb3f07c2f1227231eb49d8c4e804db_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560147101,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0e675bb3722a609b81274391f22d1c33","url_token":"chen-bai-xi-83","name":"Bruce Chen","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0e675bb3722a609b81274391f22d1c33","user_type":"people","headline":"世界非著名土木工程师","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560147101","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545813122,"updated_time":1546251439,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":33,"content":"\u003cp\u003e还有六个小时就要公开哥德巴赫猜想的证明了，期待 \u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e能证明哥德巴赫猜想还读什么书啊，你快点举世闻名了。每周去一个地方做演讲。去不同大学挂个座客教授，然后让营销号宣传宣传。这辈子钱都是滚滚而来。还读什么清华北大。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e不过刚刚看到了清华的招生广告，为了北大的生源质量，我决定放出北大招生办的联系方式。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e北京大学招生办公室\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e地址：北京大学老化学楼120室\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e邮编：100871\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e电话：010-62751407 | 010-62755074\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e传真：010-62554332\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e电子邮箱：bdzsb@pku.edu.cn\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这位同学请一定要联系。不然北大就错失了你这么好的生源。如果招生办的老师不专业。这里是北大数学系的联系方式！请你一定要联系！\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e地 址: 北京市海淀区北京大学理科1号楼\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e邮 编: 100871\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e联系电话：010-62751804\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e邮 箱：mathweb@math.pku.edu.cn\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":557695123,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"9215ccce7d3790db16cf8cb027f9adc9","url_token":"gao-rui-liang","name":"Eric G","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/2be64d3183881057829fad6e8cde8094_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/2be64d3183881057829fad6e8cde8094_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/9215ccce7d3790db16cf8cb027f9adc9","user_type":"people","headline":"戚戚于贫贱，汲汲于富贵","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/557695123","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545499994,"updated_time":1545582356,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":174,"content":"\u003cp\u003e现代数学早就过了某些人一拍脑门就能闷声搞个大新闻的年代了，你问我能不能，我的答案是当然能了，你问我这样的事情可不可能发生，我的答案是基本不可能。。。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e年轻人不要老是开这种脑洞，这本质上是对现在的数论工作者乃至数学工作者的侮辱，尽管哥德巴赫猜想现在做的人不多，但是其难度也不是一个连本科数学都没学完的人可以理解的。还是要有敬畏之心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e的确是有本科生能做出来西塔潘猜想的例子在，可是这种猜想在数学中简直多如牛毛，成为猜想可能只是单纯关注的人不多而已。（毕竟数理逻辑方面的学者本来就不是太多）\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e归根结底为什么这么多人对哥德巴赫这么有兴趣，是因为他本身的表述好懂啊，给人一种自己可以改变世界的错觉。比如说事实上更多人关注的黎曼猜想，四维六维球面的微分结构，甚至是朗兰兹纲领等等重要问题，一个水平一般的本科毕业生都看不懂这个东西在说什么，更遑论广大民科。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对前沿数学感兴趣也必须要接受科班训练，强如舒尔茨也是一个一个学位（除了速度实在有点快）拿下来的，我等凡人就没必要去做非分之想了。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559981146,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"a127e0ead5aadcd09f694aaa05863029","url_token":"Asirsar","name":"周不毅讲周易","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-78b619b07c74570b57c8ebb629f9df70_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-78b619b07c74570b57c8ebb629f9df70_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/a127e0ead5aadcd09f694aaa05863029","user_type":"people","headline":"为什么这年头想上网找个科普都能看到无数民科","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559981146","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545798852,"updated_time":1546250235,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":32,"content":"\u003cp\u003e你不会被保送，你会被请去当教授\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们不要讲的过分了，给小孩子留一点美好的幻想不好吗？至少幻想的是当数学家而不是炫富耍酷ԅ(¯ㅂ¯ԅ)\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e——————————————————\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等等鉴于题主居然是这么认真的\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我给一句忠告\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e千万不要泄露自己个人信息，不然会有你意想不到的后果\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我是觉得你这样有点太过张扬了，如果搞自己知道就行，就算发也不要在知乎。但是现在的一些人开嘲讽也真的是让人看不下去了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e听说题主高三？希望题主不要被这件事情影响了。还有就是关于哥德巴赫猜想本身，你现在不要放太多时间和精力，陈景润也说过的。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561022985,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cc59c725721c3f85e6fc869153f5bd3f","url_token":"xie-qi-87-6","name":"方鸿渐","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6849b53e53ce5349b9c4348948757210_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-6849b53e53ce5349b9c4348948757210_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/cc59c725721c3f85e6fc869153f5bd3f","user_type":"people","headline":"克莱登大学哲学博士","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561022985","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-e6f4387d99c8013746a2fd28a79fefaf_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545908518,"updated_time":1545910796,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":47,"content":"\u003cp\u003e惊闻 \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hash=\"7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$7d2c586e48e601bc6d9f7bf481ffe7a7\"\u003e@证明\u003c/a\u003e已经证明了哥德巴赫猜想，倍感欣慰。虽然我不懂数学，但这种锲而不舍的求真精神与唐僧师徒的取经精神是一样的。明年年初…正式开机…弘扬数学文化…文理两开花……多多关注。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e6f4387d99c8013746a2fd28a79fefaf_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"1412\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-66415dfface8917ca0ff4600967f43b8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e6f4387d99c8013746a2fd28a79fefaf_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1242'%20height='1412'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"1412\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-66415dfface8917ca0ff4600967f43b8_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e6f4387d99c8013746a2fd28a79fefaf_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-e6f4387d99c8013746a2fd28a79fefaf_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ab25240f80202056af6127831358ddb4_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"927\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2d95e71c4efe403060ab7b4e00042cae_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ab25240f80202056af6127831358ddb4_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1242'%20height='927'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1242\" data-rawheight=\"927\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-2d95e71c4efe403060ab7b4e00042cae_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1242\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ab25240f80202056af6127831358ddb4_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-ab25240f80202056af6127831358ddb4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-353e4bc249072cb3ca3a5c15f8e4e05f_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"394\" data-rawheight=\"430\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4591c46f7ae478a52a7caa4c93cfbcfd_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image\" width=\"394\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='394'%20height='430'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"394\" data-rawheight=\"430\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4591c46f7ae478a52a7caa4c93cfbcfd_b.jpg\" class=\"content_image lazy\" width=\"394\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-353e4bc249072cb3ca3a5c15f8e4e05f_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560858726,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0d419bed8223197f0840da9158991d6d","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560858726","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545894076,"updated_time":1545918632,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":207,"content":"\u003cp\u003e证不证明哥德巴赫猜想倒是无所谓的说，这位高中生倒是证明了知乎现在流量化,，娱乐化的问题。大家如果愿意可以点开他主页，提问5次，发表三篇文章还都是自己1月1日呀要给出论文等等的几十个字，最后居然有14000+粉。此题下众多数学界的大佬们，答出几百题也无非于此的说～\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么问题就来了，如果不是知乎给这个人流量哗众取宠，再加上大家喜欢看热闹，这样一个随便注册的号短期内能有这么高曝光量？！！既然说自己是理性，专业的问答社区，难道不应该先把这些民科号直接封掉？其实证明哥德巴赫猜想都是虚妄，不如借此机会运营知乎账号，以后再开个live，微博，公众号，自媒体联动，走向流量巅峰还实际一点的说！\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":560811545,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"2620ef3880fd5c36157285d3bee14777","url_token":"nancy-16-40-68","name":"哼哧哼哧的辭","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b4cf50a32a31b5bb96b38571f0eef7d8_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-b4cf50a32a31b5bb96b38571f0eef7d8_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/2620ef3880fd5c36157285d3bee14777","user_type":"people","headline":"开始你伟大的历险๑乛◡乛๑","badge":[],"gender":0,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/560811545","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545890056,"updated_time":1546009307,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":15,"content":"很多人在鼓励他，不要因为这次证明的结果，网友们的冷嘲热讽而改变自己对数学的初心。\u003cbr\u003e        但我看到的是一位希望借数学帮自己获取一些利益的高中生，他的初心真的是热爱纯粹的数学吗？抱歉我觉得不是。\u003cbr\u003e        他让我看到的，一方面是取巧心理在作祟。\u003cbr\u003e明明想要考上清华北大可以靠自己的努力，走很多人常规的途径，从高考考进去，但是从他个人主页显示的信息看来，他并不踏实于此。私以为，他只是一个在高中生身份中成绩平平却又想“抄近路”的人而已。\u003cbr\u003e        如果想要走和大多数人不一样的路来达到自己的目标也无可厚非，问出这样的问题只是信息缺少，想要找到招生办的老师也完全可以。但是更合理的方式应该是，提问前先让周围可能可以提供帮助的老师帮忙验证过程。而不是在知乎掀起哗然大波，再用“你们都是错的，你们等着被我打脸”的态度，和大家约定时间发布证明，一个发布前并没有给其他人验证过的证明，一个让大家抱着“看好戏”或是支持鼓励心态来等待的时间。\u003cbr\u003e问出这样的问题，眼界还是太浅。\u003cbr\u003e另一方面，则是对数学缺少敬畏。所以他的态度很容易让人觉得不舒服。哥德巴赫猜想不应该和“保送清华北大”摆在同一个地位上相提并论。（当然，我并不是说这两所大学不够顶尖。只是孰轻孰重大家都知道。）\u003cbr\u003e只是，哥德巴赫猜想应该是纯粹的，不应该被拿来和钓名沽誉的事情联系在一起的存在。\u003cbr\u003e一旦存在目的，就不对劲了。\u003cbr\u003e以上。","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561442293,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"fa44a989f73510f2663f98e515997faf","url_token":"starcraft-65-23","name":"魅影永恒","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-482766926b278db6c2bd82007c08f184_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-482766926b278db6c2bd82007c08f184_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/fa44a989f73510f2663f98e515997faf","user_type":"people","headline":"在校大学生 一个文艺的数学系渣渣","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561442293","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-069b4f26422728360ccbc68a09ea07f0_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545967887,"updated_time":1545969465,"extras":"","is_copyable":false,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":18,"content":"\u003cp\u003e既然已经最坏的恶意了，那我再深一点，看看这个头像，嘲笑与戏谑写满了丑陋的脸，这提问者是想证明一个新注册的号就可以用几千字的东西搅动知乎?证明这个自称理性的社区其实与他们轻视的别无二致?证明所谓的破万关注并非需要多少努力?如果真是这样的话，知乎怕是要从此衰落，再也没有认真答题的人了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4d7a59d9a52e7e27848e71d6db6554d4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4d7a59d9a52e7e27848e71d6db6554d4_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-20054319dfad0b521a433f071d88ed2d_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e看到大家这么踊跃的回答，大多数都抱有善意，即使是泼冷水也很有理有据的希望拯救一个迷途的孩子，在这里我就做一次恶人吧……“我向来是不惮以最坏的恶意揣测中国人的”，当我好奇点进题主的主页之后，发现他已经拿到了17k的关注……我斗胆用“最坏的恶意”揣测一下，莫不是想借着这个事情，博流量和关注的吧?2019年元旦证明发表之后无论对错想必会再有一次关注的爆发，尘埃散尽之后，这次闹剧中积累的流量或许有变现的途径?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，如果你真的证明成功的话，那我愿意为你送上真挚的祝福\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561515180,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"163a758593c98973e677a54e5a9aad36","url_token":"","name":"知乎用户","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":true},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561515180","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545974440,"updated_time":1545974890,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":23,"content":"\u003cp\u003e欢迎收看本期皇帝家的金锄头系列。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你都证明哥德巴赫猜想了还想保送去读本科？保送菲尔兹奖当教授和院士差不多，说不定北大数学院院长你35岁以前都有希望当上。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这就类似于我从六岁开始投资金融衍生品，连续20年年化收益100%，是不是可以免面试拿高盛的offer。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我凭一己之力连试验设备都不用搞出来可控核聚变商业应用方案，是不是可以去中广核拿个国企编制。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我从小学开始创业，累计创立独角兽公司20家，现在合计估值一万亿美金，这个简历能不能拿到腾讯投资部offer。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你都这水平了，不自己开个公司当大佬对得起自己的意淫么？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559483073,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"0","url_token":"","name":"匿名用户","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/0","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"follower_count":0,"is_following":false,"is_followed":false,"is_celebrity":false,"is_blocking":false,"is_blocked":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559483073","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545731024,"updated_time":1545918340,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":58,"content":"\u003cp\u003e说实话，如果一个人到高中了还自认为能够证明哥德巴赫猜想（说明他至少没有最基本的初等数论的概念），那么他上一本几乎是不可能了。至少，高考数学题里面涉及整除的部分他一定会做错；而这部分几乎是除了送分题以外全卷最简单的题。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以上论断不保证一定成立，但是几乎必然成立。\u003c/p\u003e\u003chr\u003e\u003cp\u003e更新：要不要这位同志出来PK一下？ \u003ca class=\"member_mention\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/people/c10d87a4fbf72d368d6157847990b8da\" data-hash=\"c10d87a4fbf72d368d6157847990b8da\" data-hovercard=\"p$b$c10d87a4fbf72d368d6157847990b8da\"\u003e@毛海昕\u003c/a\u003e \u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":563104367,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"cd1372650d71e6ccbed79063dceef58b","url_token":"wu-yao-wang-zhi-lei","name":"巫妖王之泪","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2c59ec55f500b8c3c560ba2ca124bc57_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2c59ec55f500b8c3c560ba2ca124bc57_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/cd1372650d71e6ccbed79063dceef58b","user_type":"people","headline":"真理追求者，世界创造者，幻想者","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/563104367","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546181844,"updated_time":1546182293,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":17,"content":"\u003cp\u003e肯定是失败，不存在成功的可能性，最微小的可能性都没有，就是零。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这没什么好说的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我想说的是，那些在评论区对他进行鼓励的人，那些对这个孩子吹鼓所谓的“梦想”的人，那些对这个孩子说什么相信自己，“他只是个孩子要鼓励”的人。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e非蠢既坏!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e当然，大多数只是蠢。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e几万人的冷嘲热讽才是正常的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这总比鼓励他，吹鼓所谓的梦想好。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这孩子最后要是成为一个民科，或者在你们所谓的鼓励之下专注哥猜忽视高考。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们很可能就把这个孩子毁了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们根本不知道证明哥猜的难度，没有对这种困扰人类智力最顶尖那群人几百年的难题有着最基本的敬畏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个高中生宣称用基本数学证明哥猜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这根本就是一种侮辱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e侮辱1742年至今为止的数学界，侮辱欧拉高数希尔伯特等等这些人类古往今来的智力最高峰。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们这种鼓励相当于对一个跑万米马拉松的新生儿喊加油。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们是在害了他。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559415028,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d5dcdb64efd495b8e8686c0f7a520947","url_token":"tao-tian-yi-64-83","name":"陶天毅","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9d5d70bc6de693cf59cd8e7c20e4338b_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-9d5d70bc6de693cf59cd8e7c20e4338b_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d5dcdb64efd495b8e8686c0f7a520947","user_type":"people","headline":"学不动了","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559415028","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545725040,"updated_time":1545725040,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":170,"content":"\u003cp\u003e从逻辑的角度看\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e若高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，则他会被清华北大数学系保送\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是一个真命题\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561255299,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"e5468a028d69b526c088ab1a6f8dcfb0","url_token":"garfield-73-55","name":"Garfield","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b412e0826dfe2f581d3314a26b1dbcff_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-b412e0826dfe2f581d3314a26b1dbcff_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/e5468a028d69b526c088ab1a6f8dcfb0","user_type":"people","headline":"ball ball CU","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561255299","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b024207495a409930582a9d543c30798_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545933645,"updated_time":1545933691,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":9,"content":"\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-31152c4ec9009223a6c4a331d02df7b7_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"688\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-877c489e5b255b9a90e30be85f0dffca_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-31152c4ec9009223a6c4a331d02df7b7_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='750'%20height='688'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"750\" data-rawheight=\"688\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-877c489e5b255b9a90e30be85f0dffca_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"750\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-31152c4ec9009223a6c4a331d02df7b7_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-31152c4ec9009223a6c4a331d02df7b7_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e回答这个问题之前 我有几个问题想问在座诸位 如果你们能回答出来 说明你们的天赋已经达到可以回答这个问题水平\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果勇士队终场得分是湖人队两倍 勇士队能否赢得这场比赛？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果我的年收入是美国gdp的十倍，我是不是世界首富？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果我能进nba名人堂 我有没有资格打cuba？\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561433325,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"1668f63980718c1f6c7fcf56a0c05992","url_token":"li-lu-yan-23","name":"醉生萌死啦","avatar_url":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6442fde1a8a39445c2c47673b3af9fa9_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-6442fde1a8a39445c2c47673b3af9fa9_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/1668f63980718c1f6c7fcf56a0c05992","user_type":"people","headline":"烟波江上屎仍稠","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561433325","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545967229,"updated_time":1545985229,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":24,"content":"\u003cp\u003e我原来写过一篇中短篇小说——《我证明了哥德巴赫猜想》，看见这个问题不禁从硬盘里挖出来，放一段开头选节。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“出来，狗杂碎，今天你也不准备讲？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e听这熟悉的声音，就知道那个狗娘养的狱警又来了，他每天都会在监狱里狂吠不止，就像个刚刚被发情的母狗一样，一边撒尿一边叫。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e稍微瞟了一眼，看到他插在腿上那根警棍上，好像又染上了些许新鲜的脑浆，不知道昨天监狱里又有多少数学家躺在他的棍下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我缓缓起身，看着他，他也看着我，他手不自觉得就握住了警棍，然后狠狠的捅了我的肚子，又甩过我的脸，我再一次倒在地上，感觉身体被一双潮湿的皮鞋肆意的践踏却无力还手。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一盆冷水浇了上来，之后就是像浇花一样一盆一盆往我脸上砸。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“你再想想，也许明天你就能记起来，你是怎么证明得哥德巴赫猜想。哦对了，今天牢房厨房的人请假了，饿的话你就做几道数学题？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e房间的铁门关上，我听见门外几个狱警发出狂笑，声音响彻整个监狱楼。他们像极了唱着欢乐颂的恶魔，一个不爽就能用那根黑色的棍子敲烂这世上绝顶聪明的脑袋。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一周前我还是这个地球上唯一能够证明出哥德巴赫猜想的人类，而现在却成了阶下囚。这不是毫无起因的无理取闹，在我的证明中，一定有他们需要的某种数学方法，只是我没有发现，而他们发现了但没弄清楚。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e接下来得几天我开始装疯卖傻，只要有狱警问我是怎么证明哥德巴赫猜想的，我就开始说胡话，就像这次这样……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“319号犯人，你现在有机会离开这里，只要你将你证明哥德巴赫猜想论文的第一百二十九页第三条的推导过程详细列展出来，你就能用智慧换取自由。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e一个狱警在我门前如是说，说的比唱的好听的多，用智慧换自由？整个监狱400多号囚犯都是数学家，要照他这么说，那研究数学的全是蠢货，都活该被关进这里？但我看这里就他一个蠢货，而且是十足的蠢货。我大声回应道：\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“319号犯人，有一点弄不明白，还门外充满智慧的狱警告诉我们，319是质数吗？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e在监狱的回音里，那个狱警竟然愣住了，过了几秒，监狱发出了一片嘶嘶的笑声，起初只是个别牢房隐隐的声音，然后整个监狱的数学家都笑了起来，越来越大声，发出就和那天那几个狱警扁完我之后一样的笑声，甚至有些老数学家笑得止不住得咳嗽。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那个狱警被我戏弄后气急败坏，疯狂用警棍敲击我的牢房的铁门，“谁再出声，我就送他上电椅!”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看那家伙快气出毛病了，就说道，“319，等于11x29，所以它不是个质数，哦，对了，那你知道29是质数么？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e监狱又一阵狂笑，那些数学家笑得比刚刚更开怀，他们就好像亲眼看到一个数论博士后做错一道小学奥数题一样开心。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e牢房的铁门钥匙孔里发出颤抖的金属摩擦声，想必是那个狱警气得钥匙都拿不稳了。他冲进来就一把将我压在墙角，之后又扯着我的头发出了门，一直走到监狱大堂中央。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我看到自己肮脏的头发丝后面，所有囚犯都透过门上的小口看着我，好像是某种送别仪式，因为大家都知道我可能活下去的机会不大了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“闭嘴，你们这群畜牲!”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他破口大骂道，“知道你们犯了什么罪被关在这里么？我不知道什么数论什么黎曼什么哥德和巴赫什么四色，我都不知道，我只知道你们犯罪了所以都他娘的该死在这里。你们读的书在这里没有任何卵用，我手里这个可能书读的太多了，所以要先你们一步去下水道发霉。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他拍了拍我的脸，然后吐了口痰在我头发里，之后在我耳边轻轻说道：“狗娘养的读书人，我最后问你一遍，你的证明过程能不能写？”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“你先回答我29是不是质数，不然我怕写了你看不懂。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e监狱里又哄堂大笑，但很声音快就停了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他拔出配枪对准我脑袋的时候，我就知道我时间不多了，也许这样对一个数学家而言，是一种屈辱的解脱。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e枪很快就响了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但意外的是，死的人不是我，而是那个狱警。他脑浆伴随着头骨在我脸上划过的时候，我感受到一个没学过什么数理知识的人的脑子，居然也是有温度的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e也许是这座监狱太冷了，所以黑暗的房间也显得保暖，血腥的味道闻起来也很温柔。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e开抢的人是个穿白褂的死鱼眼，并不是监狱的原班人马，但他看起来更邪恶更带劲，\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e“带319号去拷问室 ……”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他把大褂丢在那个狱警的尸体上，看着400多双门后的眼睛，丢下一句，“或许你们可以用他的血当墨水，记录一些数据。”\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e之后他看了看随行的狱警，眼光所及，一片避让，“把尸体放在这里，明天再搬走。”\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":562518965,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d06d14bb0d48240594d6410c1a7dca02","url_token":"ling-hu-chong-8-40","name":"令狐冲","avatar_url":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/8516699b187d93c27a334db774b77c76_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/8516699b187d93c27a334db774b77c76_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d06d14bb0d48240594d6410c1a7dca02","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/562518965","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1546096090,"updated_time":1546096090,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":19,"content":"\u003cp\u003e不成熟的人有一个特点，为了掩盖自己不能完成一个简单的事情，而假装自己在做一件很难的事情。很多人一辈子都这样。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561049716,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"7f29bcbe703d407d6b7df83ea46252ec","url_token":"ni-pan-rui","name":"AfterPhilosophy","avatar_url":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-030b56dc4fa2ab3543abd206de80cb35_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-030b56dc4fa2ab3543abd206de80cb35_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/7f29bcbe703d407d6b7df83ea46252ec","user_type":"people","headline":"动力系统博士在读/数学物理/西方哲学","badge":[],"gender":1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561049716","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545911305,"updated_time":1545911422,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":25,"content":"\u003cp\u003e入学以后去听课怕是老师在上面讲课压力都很大吧。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561735015,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"67c5aaf9a33281525d70153377c90541","url_token":"qing-nian-bu-wen-yi-10","name":"不学习毋宁死","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ca5e9da0a43ece52bdafdb848098b94_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-2ca5e9da0a43ece52bdafdb848098b94_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/67c5aaf9a33281525d70153377c90541","user_type":"people","headline":"我这么帅居然只是一个小号","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561735015","thumbnail":"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-0731a1ea0c454933ea052b1dd63f126f_200x112.jpg","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545994378,"updated_time":1546243566,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":35,"content":"\u003cp\u003e跟大家说一下，应该不用等了。看这个链接\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/53656927\" class=\"internal\"\u003e证明：一个网友的回复\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e如果真如他所说，无疑是一个民科了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e借用里面评论区朋友的一句话，如果我们大多数人都能看懂，基本上不能说错但肯定是不对的。举个例子，证明1＝0.99999999……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e用初等数学几行就解决了，我们我们还学极限做甚？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e以下是原答案\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感觉你们都忽略了另外一个可能性。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其实题主是穿越过来的，那个时候已经有人证明了，刚好他看到了，所以……\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e问下题主，你买返程票了吗？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e刚刚看了题主的主页，有了一些新的看法\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cd47caac129dcc68391afe4a14392229_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-cd47caac129dcc68391afe4a14392229_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-30a641aeecd860663a4e1fa602536bc4_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这是他比较早的动态。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e关于四面体的问题\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后再一个题目下\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cnoscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_b.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cd4bdf5c6a669f7e62f6424201bcfb07_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_r.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/noscript\u003e\u003cimg src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,\u0026lt;svg%20xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%20width='1080'%20height='1920'\u0026gt;\u0026lt;/svg\u0026gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"1920\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-cd4bdf5c6a669f7e62f6424201bcfb07_b.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-bdfec62855c1c934dd480214b0acc5fe_b.jpg\"\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个题目下的回答是哥德巴赫猜想。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们可以猜测这个问题起源他对四面体的研究。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再看看时间，最开始是三个月前，也就是九月份左右\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e你们高中尤其是高三九月份有哪些大事儿呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e奥赛。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e我们做一个大胆的猜测\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e事情是这样的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主应该高中在读。学校可能还不错，毕竟能组织奥数的应该还行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e题主的成绩应该比较偏科。数学应该是强项。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e其他科应该不行。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以题主高中前面两年把时间都搭在了奥数上面。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然而事与愿违。九月份的奥赛滑铁卢了（我们假设他是有拿奖的能力的）。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以经过深思熟虑之后，觉得自己应该是没戏了，其他科不行，数学也挂了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么办呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e怎么办呢？\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e这个时候突然想起了比赛试卷上一道关于四面体的题目，题主应该没做出来。可能的是这一题耽误了他很多时间，让他比赛失利。于是他就想把这条解出来 然后到处咨询，最后从同学哪里得知，知乎是一个985遍地走，211不如狗的高层次学术研讨平台。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e所以他看到了那个歌猜。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e转念一想，这个以前老师有提到过，感觉应该能搞出来。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e于是他就开始到处查阅相关知识点。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e通过时间线可以看出\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e他花了一个月差找资料。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e再两个月前还有一个七七八八的动态，我想在那个时候他应该有思路了，所以来放松一下。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后几天前，他把问题搞出来了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e对于这个问题，我敢肯定，他的证明肯定用了其他专业的知识，不是正面回答的，比如说我们要测体积可以用排水法。所以他才说他的方法别人看不懂。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e那么对于这种情况，他的证明基本没戏，就算是对的，哪怕若干年之后被后入证明是对的，他在现在也没什么用。因为专业的期刊不会承认的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e为什么我会有这样的想法，因为那些年我也是这样子的。那年物理奥数挂了之后，心灰意冷，感觉整个人都不好了。其他科成绩每一科都是七十分左右（包括语数英）。不过经过短暂的思考之后我觉得好好学习，奋力一搏。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e然后………………\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e等会儿再说，工头叫我过去把搅拌机弄一下。毕竟我是我们工程队最有文化的。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e感觉题主想靠这个上清北的概率应该不大了。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e但鉴于题主对于大学的向往，我这边有一个操作，可以试一下\u003c/p\u003e\u003ca data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/question/36470854/answer/511051805\" class=\"internal\"\u003e高考还有230天如何从300分冲到600分？\u003c/a\u003e\u003cp\u003e当年身边不止一个成功的案例，哪怕是现在身边也有成功的案例啊。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":561690739,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"d965a5be682e917ea1b4b55971487688","url_token":"san-shi-qiu-feng","name":"三世秋风","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/d965a5be682e917ea1b4b55971487688","user_type":"people","headline":"","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/561690739","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545989647,"updated_time":1546222418,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":23,"content":"\u003cp\u003e       兄弟，我也是一名高中生，我曾经也很骄傲，但我有自知之明，我能独立推出一元三次方程通解，能独立得出严谨的极限定义，思考出微积分很浅显的基本思想，得到了数学老师的认可，我话放在这，你要是真能证明出来，我就这辈子都服气了，服服气气的，我连牛顿，爱因斯坦都不服气，想要比一比，作为目标。你要是证出来，我将来再也不碰数学，放弃数学，你就是个天才，天才中的天才。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       正经说一下，我曾经也是一个很骄傲的人，总想做些什么，之前我得出ε-δ极限定义与微积分的基本思想后，也曾经想自己发展出整个微积分的领域，但是，我后来明白，这只是我不自量力而已，在老师推荐下，我看了高等数学的书，我才明白我的微积分思想和真正的微积分差距有多大，现代数学的发展是无数人积累的成果，我们应该有敬畏之心，我后来发誓，在不学完数学知识，就再也不碰这些玄学命题，因为这只是徒劳无功而已，我必须学习前人的智慧，戒骄戒躁，踏踏实实的去学，去思考，才是正途，想要忽视差距对我们一般人来说是不可能的，那无疑是天才中的天才，人类之子，希望能与君共勉。\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        更新\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e        这几天总感觉不对劲，我突然发现，他不是认为自己比得上那些数学家，也不是没意识到问题的难度，他只是在拼，拼运气，拼那无比渺小的几率，拼他正好发现了证明方法，就好比高尔夫选手进洞拼技术，他就像一个普通人，他也去参加高尔夫国际比赛，但他拼运气，拼他能百分百进洞，球球进洞\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       更新12月31日10点12分\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e       还有14小时我们就要见证历史了，特地留念，话说原来知乎的赞真的这么难拿，才16个赞，各位路过的没事点个赞吧\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}},{"id":559450525,"type":"answer","answer_type":"normal","question":{"type":"question","id":306537777,"title":"如果高中生能证明哥德巴赫猜想，会被清华北大数学系保送吗？","question_type":"normal","created":1545408745,"updated_time":1545408745,"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777","relationship":{}},"author":{"id":"b4df3211787dfb5619ba77b4334e7e9f","url_token":"long-shen-tian-wu","name":"龙神天舞","avatar_url":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_is.jpg","avatar_url_template":"https://pic4.zhimg.com/da8e974dc_{size}.jpg","is_org":false,"type":"people","url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/people/b4df3211787dfb5619ba77b4334e7e9f","user_type":"people","headline":"想飞上天空","badge":[],"gender":-1,"is_advertiser":false,"is_privacy":false},"url":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/answers/559450525","thumbnail":"","is_collapsed":false,"created_time":1545727960,"updated_time":1545727960,"extras":"","is_copyable":true,"is_normal":true,"voteup_count":253,"content":"\u003cp\u003e啥意思啊？只用淘宝货就造出了一颗热核聚变弹头后问能不能保送清华核物理工程专业吗？我觉得可以和清华的学生同一个教室上课，他们坐着，你前面站着。\u003c/p\u003e","relationship":{"upvoted_followees":[]}}],"paging":{"is_end":false,"is_start":false,"next":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=120\u0026sort_by=default","previous":"https://www.zhihu.com/api/v4/questions/306537777/answers?include=data%5B%2A%5D.is_normal%2Cvoteup_count%2Ccontent\u0026limit=20\u0026offset=80\u0026sort_by=default","totals":2142}}
